# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #     Adjust the window's extended style so the window appears in the taskbar and Alt+Tab.
# # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #     """
